        "action": "Require all companies to declare microplastic levels in their food & drinks",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "We urge the Government to require all companies to publicly identify and declare the amount of microplastics in their food and drink products, so people can make an informed choice about whether to consume products that may contain high levels of microplastics.",
